  "text": "Once upon a time, under the soft glow of a summer sky, two wandering travelers met for a grand adventure during the World Cup. Uruguay and Cape Verde arrived upon the field, ready to share their stories through the dance of the game. As the tale began, the air was filled with a quiet tension. A player from Cape Verde received a yellow card, and shortly after, a player from Uruguay also received a yellow card. It was a gentle reminder that even in a beautiful journey, there are rules to follow.\n\nAs the sun moved across the sky, Cape Verde found a spark of magic. With a careful shot, they found the back of the net, bringing a smile to their travelers. The score sat at zero to one, and the dream felt very close indeed. But Uruguay, filled with a quiet determination, rose to meet the moment. With a graceful header, they found their way back into the story, leveling the path for everyone. \n\nThe energy continued to flow like a calm river. Uruguay found another way through the magic of a shot, taking the lead for themselves. As they danced through the match, another player from Uruguay received a yellow card. But Cape Verde was not ready to let the story end just yet. With a steady shot, they found their rhythm once more, finding the net to make everything equal again. Even as the journey neared its end, a player from Cape Verde received a yellow card. \n\nWhen the stars finally began to peek through the clouds, the two travelers stood together, having shared every bit of their strength. The great adventure concluded in a peaceful tie of 2-2. They had traveled far, through shots and headers and many moments of grace, resting now as the world grew quiet.",
